[{},{"attrs":{"title":"API: Nuxt Modules Intro","description":"Better understand Nuxt internals"},"body":"<h1><a id=\"nuxt-internals\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#nuxt-internals\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Nuxt Internals</h1><p>Nuxt.js has a fully modular architecture which allows developers extending any part of Nuxt Core using a flexible API.</p>\n<p>Please see <a href=\"/guide/modules\">Modules Guide</a> for more detailed information if interested developing your own module.</p>\n<p>This section helps getting familiar to Nuxt internals and can be used as a reference to understand it better while writing your own modules.</p>\n<h3><a id=\"core\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#core\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Core</h3><p>These classes are the heart of Nuxt and should exist on both runtime and build time.</p>\n<h4><a id=\"nuxt\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#nuxt\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Nuxt</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/api/internals-nuxt\"><code>Nuxt</code> Class</a></li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/core/src/nuxt.js\">core/nuxt.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><a id=\"renderer\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#renderer\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Renderer</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/api/internals-renderer\"><code>Renderer</code> Class</a></li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/vue-renderer/src/renderer.js\">vue-renderer/renderer.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><a id=\"modulecontainer\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#modulecontainer\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>ModuleContainer</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/api/internals-module-container\"><code>ModuleContainer</code> Class</a></li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/core/src/module.js\">core/module.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a id=\"build\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#build\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Build</h3><p>These classes are only needed for build or dev mode.</p>\n<h4><a id=\"builder\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#builder\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Builder</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/api/internals-builder\"><code>Builder</code> Class</a></li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/builder/src/builder.js\">builder/builder.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><a id=\"generator\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#generator\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Generator</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"/api/internals-generator\"><code>Generator</code> Class</a></li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/generator/src/generator.js\">generator/generator.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a id=\"common\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#common\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Common</h3><h4><a id=\"utils\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#utils\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Utils</h4><ul>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/utils/src\">utils/src</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><a id=\"options\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#options\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Options</h4><ul>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://github.com/nuxt/nuxt.js/blob/dev/packages/config/src/options.js\">config/options.js</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a id=\"packaging-amp-usage\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#packaging-amp-usage\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Packaging &amp; Usage</h2><p>Nuxt exports all classes by default. To import them:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> { Nuxt, Builder, Utils } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'nuxt'</span></code></pre><h2><a id=\"common-patterns\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#common-patterns\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>Common patterns</h2><p>All Nuxt classes have a reference to <code>nuxt</code> instance and options, this way we always have a consistent API across classes to access <code>options</code> and <code>nuxt</code>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">SomeClass</span> </span>{\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">constructor</span> (nuxt) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">super</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.nuxt = nuxt\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.options = nuxt.options\n  }\n\n  someFunction() {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// We have access to `this.nuxt` and `this.options`</span>\n  }\n}</code></pre><p>Classes are <em>plugable</em> so they should register a plugin on main <code>nuxt</code> container to register more hooks.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">FooClass</span> </span>{\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">constructor</span> (nuxt) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">super</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.nuxt = nuxt\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.options = nuxt.options\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.nuxt.callHook(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'foo'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>)\n  }\n}</code></pre><p>So we can hook into <code>foo</code> module like this:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\">nuxt.hook(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'foo'</span>, foo =&gt; {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ...</span>\n})</code></pre>","docLink":"https://github.com/nuxt/docs/blob/master/en/api/internals.md"}]